title: Mythology - Native American Myths, Vol 4 (pdf) EarthBow
description:
This torrent contains...         (all .pdf format)

Chandler, Katherine - In the Reign of Coyote, 1905, 184 pages (Mixed)

Linderman, Frank - Indian Old-Man Stories, 1920, 223 pages (Cree and Chippewa)

Lloyd, William, Aw-aw-tan Indian Nights, 1911, 260 pages (Pima)

Dorsey, George - Traditions of the Arapaho, 1903, 492 pages (Arapaho)

Gilman, Chandler - Life on the Lakes Vol 1, 1836, 284 pages (Ojibwa)

Gilman, Chandler - Life on the Lakes Vol 2, 1836, 290 pages (Ojibwa)

Leland, Charles - Kuloskap the Master, 1902, 400 pages (Algonquin)

Lummis, Charles - The Man Who Married the Moon, 1894, 264 pages (Pueblo)

Gunn, John - Schat-Chen, 1917, 240 pages (Queres)
